Reports claim Apple has several hundred employees developing its own electric car at a secret lab. 

Speculation was rife earlier this month when an Apple-owned car was spotted driving around California fitted with Street View-style cameras. Further cars were spotted in Florida and Hawaii. 

If Apple was developing such technology, it would would rival Google's self-driving cars. 

